[SN]TITLE[SN]
Hertha BSC 0-3 Borussia Dortmund

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Borussia Dortmund set up a German Cup final meeting with Bayern Munich by easing past Hertha Berlin 3-0 in the semi-final.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gonzalo Castro opened the scoring for Dortmund in the first half, before Marco Reus and Henrikh Mkhitaryan added goals in the second half.
Bayern are currently top of the Bundesliga, seven points clear of Dortmund with four games remaining.
The cup final takes place on Saturday, 21 May at Berlin's Olympic Stadium.
